<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Charity: Water Landing Page</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css">
</head>
<body>
  <nav>
    <div class="logo">charity: water</div>
    <div class="nav-group">
      <a class="nav-link" href="#home">Home</a>
      <a class="nav-link" href="#mission">Mission</a>
      <a class="nav-link" href="#impact">Impact</a>
      <a class="nav-link" href="#stories">Stories</a>
      <a class="nav-link" href="#gallery">Gallery</a>
      <a class="nav-btn" href="#donate">Donate</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <header class="hero" id="home">
    <div class="hero-copy">
      <p class="eyebrow">Charity: Water</p>
      <h1>Clean Water Changes Everything</h1>
      <p>Millions of people around the world still lack access to clean and safe drinking water. Together, we can help provide sustainable water solutions that improve health, education, and opportunity.</p>
      <a class="hero-btn" href="#donate">Donate Now</a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section id="mission" class="section mission-section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <h2>Bringing Clean Water to Communities in Need</h2>
      <p>Charity: Water is a nonprofit organization dedicated to providing clean and safe drinking water to people living in developing countries. Through sustainable water projects and transparent reporting, the organization helps communities gain access to one of life's most basic necessities.</p>
      <div class="values-grid">
        <article class="value-card">
          <h3>Transparency</h3>
          <p>Clear reporting so donors can see the impact of every dollar.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="value-card">
          <h3>Sustainability</h3>
          <p>Projects are built to last and create reliable access to water.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="value-card">
          <h3>Community Partnership</h3>
          <p>Local leaders guide every project to ensure long-term success.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="value-card">
          <h3>Global Impact</h3>
          <p>Water systems serve entire communities and strengthen futures.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="impact" class="section impact-section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <h2>More Than Just Water</h2>
      <div class="impact-grid">
        <article class="impact-card">
          <h3>Health</h3>
          <p>Access to clean water helps prevent waterborne diseases and improves overall community health.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="impact-card">
          <h3>Education</h3>
          <p>Children spend less time collecting water and more time in school.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="impact-card">
          <h3>Opportunity</h3>
          <p>Reliable water sources allow communities to invest time in work, agriculture, and economic growth.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
      <div class="impact-summary">
        <h2>Every Donation Makes a Difference</h2>
        <ul class="impact-list">
          <li>100% of public donations fund water projects.</li>
          <li>Sustainable solutions are built to serve communities long-term.</li>
          <li>Project locations and results are shared transparently with supporters.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="stories" class="section stories-section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <h2>Stories of Change</h2>
      <div class="story-grid">
        <article class="story-card">
          <h3>Better Health</h3>
          <p>Access to clean water reduces the spread of waterborne diseases.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="story-card">
          <h3>Better Education</h3>
          <p>Children spend less time collecting water and more time learning.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="story-card">
          <h3>Better Opportunities</h3>
          <p>Communities can focus on economic growth and development.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
      <div class="story-testimonial">
        <blockquote>“Clean water changed our village. Children stay in school, and families are healthier.”</blockquote>
        <cite>— Community Leader</cite>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="gallery" class="section gallery-section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <h2>Real Stories. Real Change.</h2>
      <div class="gallery">
        <img src="/images/charitywater/charity-watch-BDZG6xjJ.jpg" alt="Community learning about a new water source">
        <img src="/images/charitywater/candid-DD7EBozV.jpg" alt="Children collecting clean water">
        <img src="/images/charitywater/charity-navigator-Caxpe_EG.jpg" alt="Volunteers working with a local partner">
        <img src="/images/charitywater/bbb-BCol5qPK.jpg" alt="Community water system infrastructure">
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="donate" class="section donate-section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <h2>Help Bring Clean Water to More Communities</h2>
      <p>Every donation supports sustainable clean water projects that create lasting change.</p>
      <a class="cta-btn" href="https://www.charitywater.org/donate" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Give Clean Water Today</a>
      <p class="donate-note">Every contribution helps fund sustainable water solutions and creates opportunities for healthier, stronger communities.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <div class="footer-copy">
      <div>
        <h3>Charity: Water</h3>
        <p>Learn more about the global water crisis and how clean water can change lives.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-nav">
        <a href="#home">Home</a>
        <a href="#mission">Mission</a>
        <a href="#impact">Impact</a>
        <a href="#stories">Stories</a>
        <a href="#gallery">Gallery</a>
        <a href="#donate">Donate</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p>© 2026 Charity: Water Landing Page Project for readme</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>